cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.MED, cs.AI, cs.IR 

The paper deals with computer-aided diagnosis techniques for lung field segmentation from chest radiographs using deep learning methods. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also proposes a deep representation learning detection mechanism and a marginal shape deep learning method, which are related to machine learning and artificial intelligence, making cs.LG (Machine Learning) another likely category. The paper also deals with medical imaging and diagnosis, making cs.MED (Medical Imaging) a likely category. Additionally, the paper proposes a new approach to shape deformation parameter estimation, which could be related to information retrieval, making cs.IR (Information Retrieval) a possible category.
